---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Leone Consulting: Method, Expertise and Delivery" description="Learn about Leone Consulting's method, experience and technical expertise: a science-driven approach to AI and software delivery focused on measurable outcomes.">
  <Header />
  
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About Us</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We are a team of technology-passionate professionals, specialized in AI Engineering, 
            software development and IT consulting.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission -->
    <section class="py-20 px-6">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">Our Mission</h2>
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p class="text-xl mb-6">
              Leone Consulting was born from a passion for technological innovation and the desire to 
              help companies make the most of the opportunities offered by artificial intelligence 
              and digital transformation.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl mb-6">
              Our mission is to provide cutting-edge technological solutions that solve real problems, 
              improve business processes and create measurable value for our clients.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl">
              We strongly believe in code quality, solid architecture and a pragmatic approach 
              to problem solving. Every project is an opportunity to excel and 
              build lasting relationships based on trust and results.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Values -->
    <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-16 text-center">Our Values</h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Innovation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We are always at the forefront with the latest technologies and methodologies, 
              continuously exploring new solutions to offer the best to our clients.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Excellence</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We always aim for excellence in everything we do, from the code we write 
              to communication with clients, ensuring high quality standards.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Collaboration</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We believe in the power of collaboration. We work closely with our 
              clients to fully understand their needs and build tailored solutions.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Scientific Method</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We rigorously apply the scientific method to IT and AI projects: data-driven analysis, 
              verifiable hypotheses, and measurable results. We don't improvise, we document every choice.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Expertise -->
    <section class="py-20 px-6">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Our Expertise</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-12">
            Years of experience in projects of varying complexity have allowed us to develop 
            solid skills in various technological areas.
          </p>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-left">
            <div class="bg-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">AI & Machine Learning</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
                <li>• Deep Learning</li>
                <li>• NLP & Computer Vision</li>
                <li>• LLM Integration</li>
                <li>• MLOps</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Software Development</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
                <li>• Python, JavaScript, TypeScript</li>
                <li>• React, Vue, Astro</li>
                <li>• Node.js, FastAPI</li>
                <li>• SQL/NoSQL Databases</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Cloud & DevOps</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
                <li>• AWS, Azure, GCP</li>
                <li>• Docker & Kubernetes</li>
                <li>• CI/CD Pipelines</li>
                <li>• Infrastructure as Code</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-primary-600 text-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Want to know more?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-primary-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Contact us to discuss your project and discover how we can help you.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/en/contact" 
          class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-white text-primary-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all transform hover:scale-105 font-semibold shadow-lg"
        >
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
